                                </StackLayout>
                                <Label Text="Nadya and Sasha - the two main protagonists in this very educational story - also had a great chemistry, I think, making the movie extra-special. This film is also a great testament of resilience in the face of adversity, and the unshakeable belief in the power of the human spirit; reminding us that we have the magic power, to manifest dreams, love and positive change!&#10;" TextColor="#37383b" FontSize="15" CharacterSpacing="0.2" />

